with these gauche Americans.

403
00:22:27,763 --> 00:22:29,890
Yes, yes, yes, yes. Yes.

404
00:22:31,350 --> 00:22:32,601
Yes.

405
00:22:34,227 --> 00:22:35,312
Yes.

